It's because they feel guilty and scared.

00:03:08.240 --> 00:03:08.960
Twelve.

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:12.440
Let's find the Japanese tomorrow.

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:14.240
Even if we can't help him,

00:03:14.240 --> 00:03:15.640
Wu Zhen,

00:03:16.360 --> 00:03:18.560
We can't go back empty-handed.

00:03:18.560 --> 00:03:19.360
Don't worry.

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:21.760
Leng Zi. Deyou.

