What can I do for you?

00:03:30.280 --> 00:03:33.079
We know Wu Zhen and Shangguan Eagle.

00:03:33.079 --> 00:03:34.160
Let's take a walk.

00:03:34.480 --> 00:03:35.040
Okay.

00:03:35.040 --> 00:03:36.720
We might run into each other.

00:03:37.079 --> 00:03:38.000
But

00:03:38.200 --> 00:03:40.000
in front of Shangguan Bao,

00:03:42.320 --> 00:03:44.280
in front of Shangguan Bao.

00:03:45.400 --> 00:03:47.280
Except me,

00:03:47.600 --> 00:03:51.120
can only be called Old Leopard.

00:03:51.400 --> 00:03:54.400
You all respect me.

00:03:54.920 --> 00:03:56.160
Yes.

00:03:57.680 --> 00:03:59.240
Are you really willing

00:04:00.200 --> 00:04:02.920
will you give it to him willingly?

