Otherwise,

00:04:11.160 --> 00:04:13.280
I'll have to fight him one day.

00:04:15.080 --> 00:04:16.720
But in this situation,

00:04:17.040 --> 00:04:18.760
even ten Huo Lang

00:04:18.760 --> 00:04:20.800
can't stand a Shangguan Bao.

00:04:21.240 --> 00:04:22.440
To be honest,

00:04:22.640 --> 00:04:24.760
thanks to them

00:04:24.760 --> 00:04:26.440
thanks to them.

