Just us.

00:04:28.360 --> 00:04:32.360
We are just a few brave bandits.

00:04:34.080 --> 00:04:35.400
Let me tell you.

00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:37.880
I don't care if you go out to eat, drink and gamble.

00:04:38.320 --> 00:04:40.920
Old Leopard wants to pick a fight with you.

00:04:40.920 --> 00:04:42.560
With me here,

00:04:42.560 --> 00:04:44.280
