00:05:14.280 --> 00:05:17.440
It’s the real handwriting of Qinghe invitation.

00:05:23.200 --> 00:05:24.160
Mr. Zhang.

00:05:24.520 --> 00:05:26.720
Although these things are not real money,

00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:27.600
but

00:05:28.960 --> 00:05:30.880
It's priceless.

