00:05:37.080 --> 00:05:38.720
Wen Kui, you...

00:05:38.960 --> 00:05:40.560
Why are you so generous?

00:05:40.760 --> 00:05:43.720
I always thought you were an expert in war.

00:05:44.240 --> 00:05:45.760
