00:06:45.280 --> 00:06:46.240
Brigade Commander.

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:48.120
Look at him.

00:06:48.320 --> 00:06:49.920
I really want to shoot him.

00:06:51.240 --> 00:06:53.480
That's why we lost the war.

00:06:56.360 --> 00:06:57.080
Brigade Commander.

00:06:57.440 --> 00:06:59.240
The paintings you gave him are so valuable.

00:06:59.560 --> 00:07:01.040
