00:07:02.760 --> 00:07:04.360
Those calligraphy and paintings are valuable,

00:07:04.360 --> 00:07:05.800
but not many people know it.

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:08.280
Money is still useful now.

00:07:08.480 --> 00:07:09.480
Leave it.

00:07:10.960 --> 00:07:11.800
Brigade Commander.

00:07:12.680 --> 00:07:13.960
How is the prevention of the epidemic?

00:07:13.960 --> 00:07:15.080
Basically under control.

00:07:15.360 --> 00:07:17.880
All the virus have been placed in the pit.

00:07:20.200 --> 00:07:21.800
Everyone in the county

00:07:21.800 --> 00:07:23.120
You have to be careful, okay?

