By the way, there's another big problem.

00:07:25.960 --> 00:07:26.680
Go ahead.

00:07:26.920 --> 00:07:28.720
I heard that swordsmen came here too.

00:07:29.160 --> 00:07:30.680
Is there an epidemic over there?

00:07:31.320 --> 00:07:32.760
I almost forgot.

00:07:33.640 --> 00:07:34.920
Captain Zhu. Yes.

00:07:34.920 --> 00:07:36.040
Follow me to Black Tiger Mountain. Yes.

00:07:36.280 --> 00:07:36.960
Let's go.

00:08:06.800 --> 00:08:07.800
Lieutenant Colonel.

00:08:35.360 --> 00:08:37.720
I'll send you some books tomorrow.

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:39.320
Stay here.

00:08:39.320 --> 00:08:40.200
Don't run around.

00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:43.640
Someone will cook for you these days.

00:08:44.039 --> 00:08:45.880
and the doctor will give you a checkup.

00:08:46.560 --> 00:08:48.200
I'll take you back to Shaanxi

00:08:48.640 --> 00:08:49.960
I'll take you back to Shaanxi.

00:08:50.520 --> 00:08:51.360
I see.

