00:09:28.680 --> 00:09:29.680
Study hard.

00:09:30.040 --> 00:09:32.320
You can help a lot of people when you grow up.

00:09:32.720 --> 00:09:33.720
But here,

00:09:33.880 --> 00:09:35.680
I can only read the books the Japanese gave me.

00:09:36.480 --> 00:09:37.840
There's no good or bad in books.

00:09:38.080 --> 00:09:39.520
The key is those who read.

00:09:40.240 --> 00:09:41.960
Have you read a lot?

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:43.720
Not really.

00:09:44.280 --> 00:09:46.120
Get some rest. I'm going out to find someone.

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:49.360
Are you coming back?

00:09:50.400 --> 00:09:51.160
Of course.

00:09:58.280 --> 00:09:59.880
As Mr. Taniwara said,

00:10:00.120 --> 00:10:02.960
