00:10:03.720 --> 00:10:06.160
But we've wasted too much time

00:10:06.280 --> 00:10:06.960
too much time.

00:10:07.400 --> 00:10:08.960
Weapons and supplies

00:10:09.320 --> 00:10:11.360
are no longer an absolute advantage.

00:10:11.840 --> 00:10:12.960
So...

00:10:12.960 --> 00:10:15.160
This is not good for us.

00:10:15.160 --> 00:10:17.080
We need to speed up the pace

00:10:17.480 --> 00:10:19.840
and block all the routes in Yunmenma.

00:10:20.080 --> 00:10:22.080
What do you think, Mr. Tanihara?

00:10:22.080 --> 00:10:23.960
Colonel is right.

00:10:24.880 --> 00:10:28.440
Choi Moon-Kui is busy dealing with the epidemic.

00:10:29.080 --> 00:10:32.720
But the Chinese army that withdrew from Fuyang

00:10:32.800 --> 00:10:34.240
