00:10:59.360 --> 00:11:00.200
In Shanzhou,

00:11:00.520 --> 00:11:01.960
I made them

00:11:01.960 --> 00:11:03.520
to provoke them twice.

00:11:04.080 --> 00:11:04.960
But in the end,

00:11:05.200 --> 00:11:07.600
