00:11:13.840 --> 00:11:14.720
Yes.

00:11:15.320 --> 00:11:17.560
That's why I've been doing this.

00:11:18.680 --> 00:11:21.240
Colonel, I have another request.

00:11:21.440 --> 00:11:22.240
Go ahead.

00:11:22.600 --> 00:11:24.640
Please withdraw

00:11:24.840 --> 00:11:25.840
