00:11:26.080 --> 00:11:28.840
Make it look like the Imperial Army won't go west.

00:11:28.840 --> 00:11:31.400
That way, I have more chances

00:11:31.400 --> 00:11:33.480
to drive a wedge between them.

00:12:58.680 --> 00:12:59.520
Hurry up.

00:13:30.280 --> 00:13:31.040
Fool.

00:13:33.640 --> 00:13:34.480
Where is he?

00:13:34.640 --> 00:13:35.760
He said he went out for a walk.

00:13:37.160 --> 00:13:38.800
He's still young.

00:13:39.440 --> 00:13:40.560
I can't sit still.

00:13:41.760 --> 00:13:42.960
But it's good.

00:13:43.360 --> 00:13:47.120
Maybe we can kill some Japanese out there. Yes.

00:13:53.400 --> 00:13:54.240
Who is it?

00:13:55.280 --> 00:13:56.200
It's me.

00:13:56.400 --> 00:13:57.400
Translator Pang.

00:14:01.160 --> 00:14:02.160
Coming.

00:14:09.920 --> 00:14:11.200
You're still up so late.

00:14:11.440 --> 00:14:12.360
I'm here to see you.

00:14:13.960 --> 00:14:16.520
Come on. What are you taking?

