00:14:39.880 --> 00:14:42.000
The 100,000 swordsmen are very powerful.

00:14:42.280 --> 00:14:44.600
I didn't expect to see you here today.

00:14:45.480 --> 00:14:46.520
It's an honor.

00:14:46.720 --> 00:14:48.160
Bottoms up. Bottoms up.

00:14:48.160 --> 00:14:49.480
Wait, wait, wait.

00:14:49.840 --> 00:14:51.760
No, put the wine down.

00:14:53.640 --> 00:14:55.760
We have something to ask you.

00:14:56.400 --> 00:14:58.480
You are also knowledgeable.

00:14:58.760 --> 00:15:01.600
Now you work for the Japanese.

00:15:02.160 --> 00:15:03.240
We want to know

00:15:03.480 --> 00:15:06.680
