00:15:12.400 --> 00:15:14.920
It depends on your request.

00:15:16.800 --> 00:15:18.400
Of course.

00:15:18.400 --> 00:15:19.920
It's not for wealth,

00:15:19.920 --> 00:15:21.640
not for a few more wives.

00:15:21.640 --> 00:15:24.120
Who would do this for the Japanese?

00:15:26.440 --> 00:15:28.720
What if it's for survival?

00:15:30.000 --> 00:15:31.880
You mean

00:15:32.120 --> 00:15:33.520
you can't live

00:15:36.720 --> 00:15:39.160
without working with the Japanese?

00:15:39.520 --> 00:15:40.240
Deyou.

00:15:40.280 --> 00:15:42.080
It's not appropriate to say that.

00:15:42.200 --> 00:15:43.600
What do you mean?

00:15:43.760 --> 00:15:45.120
Since we're here,

00:15:45.120 --> 00:15:46.640
We have to ask him.

00:15:46.640 --> 00:15:49.200
The more we ask, the more sincere we are.

00:15:49.840 --> 00:15:51.480
Am I right? Yes.

00:15:51.480 --> 00:15:53.520
Just tell me what you want.

00:15:53.840 --> 00:15:55.840
I'll tell General Teng Gang the truth.

00:15:55.840 --> 00:15:57.000
Don't interrupt.

00:15:57.160 --> 00:15:58.480
You haven't told us

00:15:58.480 --> 00:16:00.240
