00:16:00.240 --> 00:16:02.480
What's the good of being a lackey?

00:16:13.920 --> 00:16:15.000
I almost killed him.

00:16:17.440 --> 00:16:18.440
Almost what?

00:16:22.240 --> 00:16:23.840
Look at him.

00:16:23.840 --> 00:16:25.360
Can you be a lackey?

00:16:25.640 --> 00:16:26.920
I almost killed a dog.

00:16:27.840 --> 00:16:30.800
There are fewer people in Luoyang, but there are many dogs.

00:16:30.800 --> 00:16:32.160
There are plenty of opportunities to kill.

00:16:32.680 --> 00:16:33.640
What are you waiting for?

00:16:33.640 --> 00:16:34.880
Didn't you see the guest?

00:16:34.880 --> 00:16:36.600
Sit down and drink with the guest.

00:16:46.160 --> 00:16:47.080
Come on, bro.

00:16:48.560 --> 00:16:49.480
Come on.

00:16:50.720 --> 00:16:52.760
We haven't agreed yet.

00:16:54.200 --> 00:16:55.120
Logically,

00:16:55.520 --> 00:16:57.320
the second head of the Xidao

00:16:57.320 --> 00:16:58.480
can ask for a lot of money.

00:16:58.960 --> 00:17:01.280
No, no, no. We don't offer a price.

00:17:01.560 --> 00:17:03.760
It depends on the price the Japanese offer.

00:17:03.760 --> 00:17:05.280
It's a good price.

00:17:05.280 --> 00:17:06.760
We'll follow them.

00:17:06.760 --> 00:17:08.280
If the price is not right,

00:17:08.280 --> 00:17:09.920
