00:17:13.000 --> 00:17:14.440
Isn't that good?

00:17:15.240 --> 00:17:17.880
But you have to give me a bottom line.

00:17:19.119 --> 00:17:20.400
to get something from me.

00:17:20.720 --> 00:17:21.720
Listen.

00:17:22.040 --> 00:17:24.760
I have a condition. I'll tell the Japanese too.

00:17:24.760 --> 00:17:26.079
Why should I tell you?

00:17:26.079 --> 00:17:27.560
You're just a messenger.

00:17:27.560 --> 00:17:29.560
Can you take the responsibility if I tell you?

00:17:30.400 --> 00:17:32.320
That's good. That's easy for me.

00:17:32.760 --> 00:17:34.480
I'll take my leave.

00:17:34.480 --> 00:17:37.360
Please close the door from outside.

00:17:41.760 --> 00:17:43.320
Brother, let me see him off.

00:17:48.920 --> 00:17:49.760
What happened?

00:17:50.720 --> 00:17:51.760
Don't mention it.

00:17:54.080 --> 00:17:56.640
I wanted to see the way in and out.

00:17:57.000 --> 00:18:00.360
but there were so many patrol guards.

00:18:01.000 --> 00:18:02.080
At this moment,

00:18:02.400 --> 00:18:04.360
I suddenly saw a lonely ghost.

00:18:04.840 --> 00:18:06.720
It happened to feed my sword.

00:18:07.520 --> 00:18:10.560
I didn't expect him to be so stubborn.

00:18:11.480 --> 00:18:12.200
Where is he?

00:18:13.080 --> 00:18:13.720
He ran away.

00:18:14.160 --> 00:18:15.920
If it weren't for the patrol,

00:18:16.240 --> 00:18:17.680
he wouldn't have escaped.

00:18:18.680 --> 00:18:19.240
No.

00:18:20.400 --> 00:18:21.800
You patrol ghost.

00:18:23.000 --> 00:18:24.680
Why do I feel that

00:18:24.680 --> 00:18:26.080
not very smooth?

00:18:29.920 --> 00:18:31.720
You want to kill a ghost?

00:18:32.560 --> 00:18:35.120
The ghost's patrol team is here.

00:18:36.440 --> 00:18:38.920
The devil ran away.

00:18:40.320 --> 00:18:42.040
That means the person you want to kill

00:18:42.040 --> 00:18:43.080
is not a demon.

00:18:44.400 --> 00:18:45.320
That's right.

00:18:45.320 --> 00:18:47.240
Why didn't I figure it out?

00:18:48.400 --> 00:18:50.960
How could you go out with that brain of yours?

00:18:50.960 --> 00:18:53.120
Stay at home from now on.

00:18:53.680 --> 00:18:54.520
Stop drinking.

00:18:55.920 --> 00:18:56.760
Wake up.

00:18:59.640 --> 00:19:01.160
Let's have some tea in that room.

00:19:11.480 --> 00:19:12.480
Put on your clothes.

00:19:12.640 --> 00:19:13.760
No, you wear it.

00:19:13.960 --> 00:19:14.680
No, I'm not cold.

00:19:14.920 --> 00:19:16.080
Put it on.

00:19:16.640 --> 00:19:17.480
Hurry up.

00:19:47.280 --> 00:19:48.040
Hurry!

00:19:52.480 --> 00:19:53.640
So many devils' cars.

00:19:54.360 --> 00:19:56.440
Are they going to hit Shanzhou?

00:19:56.960 --> 00:19:57.840
No.

00:19:58.080 --> 00:19:59.800
They are heading to Luoyang.

00:20:00.440 --> 00:20:03.120
These should be removed from Shaanxi.

00:20:03.920 --> 00:20:04.800
What do you mean?

00:20:05.200 --> 00:20:06.000
I quit.

00:20:08.800 --> 00:20:09.920
It doesn't make sense.

00:20:21.760 --> 00:20:23.360
We've been here all night.

00:20:23.800 --> 00:20:24.760
