Go ahead.

00:37:06.440 --> 00:37:07.280
By the way,

00:37:07.960 --> 00:37:09.880
let me make it clear first.

00:37:09.880 --> 00:37:11.280
I have a problem.

00:37:11.760 --> 00:37:13.000
I'm working.

00:37:13.000 --> 00:37:14.800
No matter they are happy or not,

00:37:14.800 --> 00:37:16.200
I have to be happy first.

00:37:16.200 --> 00:37:17.760
If I'm unhappy,

00:37:17.760 --> 00:37:19.720
I'll leave.

00:37:19.960 --> 00:37:21.680
I'll put it bluntly.

00:37:22.240 --> 00:37:23.600
Please forgive me.

00:37:30.240 --> 00:37:31.560
Don't worry, Young Master Huo.

00:37:32.080 --> 00:37:33.240
Here,

00:37:33.520 --> 00:37:35.920
I can guarantee your freedom of action.

00:37:36.800 --> 00:37:38.720
Don't say that.

00:37:39.040 --> 00:37:42.600
My parents gave me the freedom to act.

00:38:43.400 --> 00:38:46.160
You bastard! You don't even let the children go!

00:38:47.080 --> 00:38:49.040
I want to chop them into minced meat.

00:38:52.160 --> 00:38:53.720
Our priority now

