So,

00:39:53.920 --> 00:39:55.080
during this period,

00:39:55.240 --> 00:39:57.160
bind your men.

00:39:57.440 --> 00:39:59.840
You'll be fine if you don't go down the mountain.

00:40:00.400 --> 00:40:01.440
No.

00:40:02.320 --> 00:40:03.120
No.

00:40:03.520 --> 00:40:05.440
We have over 30,000 men

00:40:05.440 --> 00:40:07.040
to live on air?

00:40:07.560 --> 00:40:08.440
Yes.

00:40:12.200 --> 00:40:12.880
How about this?

00:40:14.160 --> 00:40:15.520
300 antidotes

00:40:15.720 --> 00:40:17.120
and 100 vaccines.

00:40:17.440 --> 00:40:18.520
If possible,

00:40:18.520 --> 00:40:20.040
I'll send it to you tomorrow.

00:40:21.200 --> 00:40:22.080
Look.

00:40:22.280 --> 00:40:23.640
I thought

00:40:23.920 --> 00:40:26.320
I'm the only one who's shameless.

00:40:26.560 --> 00:40:28.680
You are better than me.

00:40:28.840 --> 00:40:29.760
Enough, Mr. Huo.

00:40:30.200 --> 00:40:31.440
That's enough.

00:40:31.800 --> 00:40:33.760
It shows the sincerity of the Imperial Army.

00:40:33.760 --> 00:40:36.080
Be content.

00:40:36.280 --> 00:40:38.000
Easy for you to say.

00:40:38.160 --> 00:40:39.960
If you feel itchy one day,

00:40:40.480 --> 00:40:42.760
throw some rats here,

00:40:42.960 --> 00:40:44.520
How many people will die?

00:40:45.360 --> 00:40:46.560
So,

00:40:47.560 --> 00:40:49.800
you won't die

00:40:51.360 --> 00:40:52.800
you won't die.

00:40:54.280 --> 00:40:55.840
Mr. Huo, harmony is the most important.

00:40:56.120 --> 00:40:57.120
The most important thing

